sources.description:
Ghost fingers pressed the trigger - and death flashed from the shadows...
When a sudden spurt of murders occurs in Texas Big Bend country, suspicion immediately falls on a young drifter who just moved to the area.

Original title: High Lonesome (1950) 
Director & Writer: Alan Le May
Actors: John Drew Barrymore, Chill Wills, John Archer, Kristine Miller 
Genres: Classics, Western

00:00 Full Movie
